            Collège Sacré Coeur de Mortain
        </h3>
        <ul class="p-0 list-none">
            <li class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg mb-4 border border-slate-200 last:mb-0 gap-2">
